      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $I(x) =  \\int_{t=0}^{+\\infty} e^{-t^2}\\cos(2xt)\\,d t$.\n    Prouver que $I$ est de classe $\\mathcal{C}^1$ sur $\\R$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I(x) =  \\int_{t=0}^{+\\infty} e^{-t^2}\\cos(2xt)\\,d t\\)</span>. Prouver que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span> est de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^1\\)</span> sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\R\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9cfeae43-8bfa-4a2a-ba82-ba03b7d1c02f",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher une relation simple entre $I$ et $I'$.",
        "html": "<p>Chercher une relation simple entre <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I&#39;\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "677a4f24-2a86-465d-9872-acdecd238f41",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire la valeur de $I(x)$\n    $\\Bigl($on admet que $I(0) = \\frac{\\sqrt\\pi}2\\Bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p>En déduire la valeur de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I(x)\\)</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Bigl(\\)</span>on admet que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I(0) = \\frac{\\sqrt\\pi}2\\Bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7da572be-ae72-4588-b0ab-af79eb32930d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$I'(x) = -2xI(x)$.\n$I(x) = \\frac{\\sqrt\\pi}2 e^{-x^2}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(I&#39;(x) = -2xI(x)\\)</span>. <span class=\"math inline\">\\(I(x) = \\frac{\\sqrt\\pi}2 e^{-x^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
